<h1 id="-publishdestroy-id-request-options-">.publishDestroy( <code>{id}</code>, [<code>request</code>], [<code>options</code>] )</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>Publish the destruction of a model</p>
